x.html&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHlGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=47a3feb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2⃣💝貼心提示：<br />\n拘捕後直接過堂嘅手足，袋可能被狗仔咬爛咗，大家見到不妨遞個有色膠袋或者環保袋比佢哋啦<br />\n<br />\n3⃣☔️遮陣接送<br />\n保釋處理：將由正門離開，保釋手續需時，請耐心等候，可幫手足call定的士， 遮陣接送手足亦可先向家屬溝通， 避免誤會<br />\n<br />\n4⃣🚓還押送車<br />\n還押處理手足，將由側門 / 停車場離開，可等懲教車送車<br />\nP.S. 懲教不是POPO唔好屌佢哋"},{"pid":"92b6de8b3a6d734593ac88b3722fd92a9d3da9f4","tid":2069701,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:49:31.000Z","msg":"詳情可follow被捕人士關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHlGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=bb4718fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\nIG<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyouarenotalonehk%3Figshid%3Dknzk6gr75kea&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHlGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=ca33d390\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea</a>"},{"pid":"6868deacc0b2ef69b8cabb05d52e3971747604cc","tid":2069701,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:49:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h8Eyvjw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh8Eyvjw.jpg&h=0e60d17f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"800bf46cc2db7bf6e97b25242baf600176ac30f6","tid":2069701,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:49:54.000Z","msg":"【司法機關政務處公告】- 11/02/2020<br />\n<br />\n基於公共衞生的考慮，由 2020 年 2 月 13 日起司法機構 將實施以下安排:-<br />\n<br />\n<strong>體溫檢測</strong><br />\n- 所有人均須接受體溫檢測<br />\n- 發燒或拒絕接受檢測人士不得進入<br />\n<br />\n<strong>法庭座位安排</strong><br />\n- 公眾席的座位數目將減少約一半<br />\n- 取消站立旁聽聆訊<br />\n- 將會使用較大的法庭，並在可行情況下